# Treat generated/binary assets as binary so git doesn't line-diff them as
# text. The pre-push review hook reads the diff via strict UTF-8 and crashes
# on raw PDF/image bytes; marking them binary makes git emit "Binary files
# differ" instead. public/brochure.pdf is regenerated from src — never merge it.
*.pdf binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
